msgstr "首先执行 `rw [h]` 将 `y` 替换为 `x + 7`。"

#: Game.Levels.Tutorial.L02rw
msgid "Can you take it from here? Click on \"Show more help!\" if you need a hint."
msgstr "你能从这里开始吗？如果您需要提示，请点击 \"显示更多帮助！\"。"

#: Game.Levels.Tutorial.L02rw
msgid "Now `rfl` will work."
msgstr "现在 `rfl` 可以工作了。"

#: Game.Levels.Tutorial.L02rw
