"what `37 ^ (succ d)` is, given only `37 ^ d`.\n"
"\n"
"You can probably guess the names of the general theorems:\n"
"\n"
"  * `pow_zero (a : ℕ) : a ^ 0 = 1`\n"
"  * `pow_succ (a b : ℕ) : a ^ succ b = a ^ b * a`\n"
"\n"
